    "testimonials": {
      "title": "What people say about us.",
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "Vitalik Buterin",
          "role": "Aztec foundation",
          "image": "/assets/profile-vitalik.png",
          "quote": "The balance between Transparency and Privacy, accountable and unaccountable, manifest and secret, convex and concave, 1 and 0 is one of the most fun puzzles blockchain tech has to solve for the world. W3P community approaches this with incredible humility and a unravel-the-knot open debate approach. Also I like how they dress."
        },
        {
          "name": "Vitalik Buterin",
          "role": "Aztec foundation",
          "image": "/assets/profiles/aya-miyaguchi.png",
          "quote": "I appreciate Web3 Privacy Now for upholding Cypherpunk values, which are at the core of the Web3 movement. In a space increasingly influenced by hyper-financialization, having an organization dedicated to principles that distinguish Web3 from Wall Street serves as a crucial guiding light."
        },
        {
          "name": "Vitalik Buterin",
          "role": "Aztec foundation",
          "image": "/assets/profiles/kurt-opsahl.png",
          "quote": "W3N reminds us daily of why we are here. Privacy, a basic human right, beats at the heart of the cypherpunk ethos and everything worth building. Their conferences gather dreamers, rebels, visionaries and long-term thinkers."
        },
        {
          "name": "Vitalik Buterin",
          "role": "Aztec foundation",
          "image": "/assets/profiles/richard-stallman.png",
          "quote": "Over the last two years, I mostly stepped away from crypto events, feeling disconnected from the nihilistic short-term focus dominating much of the space. Then I found Web3PrivacyNow. They managed to amplify the cypherpunk voice within the cryptocurrency space, proving it is not just alive but growing stronger."
        },
        {
          "name": "Vitalik Buterin",
          "role": "Aztec foundation",
          "image": "/assets/profile-vitalik.png",
          "quote": "The balance between Transparency and Privacy, accountable and unaccountable, manifest and secret, convex and concave, 1 and 0 is one of the most fun puzzles blockchain tech has to solve for the world. W3P community approaches this with incredible humility."
        },
        {
          "name": "Vitalik Buterin",
          "role": "Aztec foundation",
          "image": "/assets/profile-vitalik.png",
          "quote": "The balance between Transparency and Privacy, accountable and unaccountable, manifest and secret, convex and concave, 1 and 0 is one of the most fun puzzles blockchain tech has to solve for the world."
        },
        {
          "name": "Vitalik Buterin",
          "role": "Aztec foundation",
          "image": "/assets/profiles/kurt-opsahl.png",
          "quote": "W3N reminds us daily of why we are here. Privacy is a basic human right. Their conferences are a gathering place for the uncompromising builders and the long-term thinkers. These are my people, creating a future that remembers what matters."
        },
        {
          "name": "Vitalik Buterin",
          "role": "Aztec foundation",
          "image": "/assets/profile-vitalik.png",
          "quote": "The balance between Transparency and Privacy is not abstract here. This community turns it into practical discussion, grounded tradeoffs, and real tools that people can use right now."
        },
        {
          "name": "Vitalik Buterin",
          "role": "Aztec foundation",
          "image": "/assets/profiles/aya-miyaguchi.png",
          "quote": "I appreciate Web3 Privacy Now for keeping the cypherpunk mission clear while the ecosystem changes fast. It is one of the few spaces that consistently keeps principles first."
        },
        {
          "name": "Vitalik Buterin",
          "role": "Aztec foundation",
          "image": "/assets/profiles/richard-stallman.png",
          "quote": "W3PN bridges policy, tech and culture. It is one of the few spaces where those worlds consistently collaborate in concrete ways."
        },
        {
          "name": "Vitalik Buterin",
          "role": "Aztec foundation",
          "image": "/assets/profile-vitalik.png",
          "quote": "Their workshops are clear, direct and effective. People leave with practical tools they can use immediately across projects and communities."
        },
        {
          "name": "Vitalik Buterin",
          "role": "Aztec foundation",
          "image": "/assets/profile-vitalik.png",
          "quote": "The ecosystem map and open archives are incredibly useful for onboarding contributors and helping newcomers understand where they can participate."
        }
      ]
    },
